7.22	Natan_Slifkin	Natan Slifkin	Natan Slifkin (also Nosson Slifkin) (born 25 June 1975 in Manchester, England), also popularly known as the "Zoo Rabbi", is a British-born Israeli ordained but non-pulpit serving Orthodox rabbi best known for his interest in zoology, science and for his books on these topics, which are controversial in the Haredi world.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c1/Slifkin.jpg/200px-Slifkin.jpg
